QSvgStyle
---------
* Rework animation framework

* scrollbars: add pgup/pgdown buttons option
* lineedit : minimum width should be sufficient to show placeholder text
* add ability to animate non busy progress bars
* add ability for widgets to alter qsvgstyle theme config by using
  dynamic widget properties. e.g. qsvgstyle.frame.width=3
* replace dir,orn pair by a rot/flip variable
* renderElement: should take into account dir,orn

QSvgThemeBuilder
----------------
* add magnifier tool
* add measure tool/tracer
* replace manual populated list of elements by an automatic method
  like the one used by stylemanager

QSvgThemeManager
----------------
* switch to QtPropertyBrowser from Qt Solutions
